{"tid":1814960,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD 正式發佈地表最強 Ryzen Threadripper 3990X處理器","createTime":"2020-01-07T07:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T03:37:48.000Z","uid":28114,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd580809009f249cbaf5f261992a1b1b53d8c28","tid":1814960,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"【CES2020】AMD 正式發佈地表最強 Ryzen Threadripper 3990X處理器，擁有 64核心、支援 128線程，2.9GHz Base Clock、4.3GHz Boost Clock，高達 288MB Cache，最高 TDP 為 250W，定價為 US$3,990，2 月 7 日上市。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ejZ3zX2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FejZ3zX2.jpg&h=e1a1d4ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/94338753945/posts/10156920489513946/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F94338753945%2Fposts%2F10156920489513946%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=cb3fedbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/94338753945/posts/10156920489513946/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"25e17a26ad76e8290611fe86e93500c140dde844","tid":1814960,"uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:25:54.000Z","msg":"AMD yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9635d970e73642146c62cd787025184bcff4e723","tid":1814960,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:26:35.000Z","msg":"250w...."},{"pid":"60b74ea4485a2c69c5d74b4c1889395ac1e32bff","tid":1814960,"uid":188421,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"見到64核 同200幾MB cache 就諗起以前轉第一部windows XP機 4核160GB hard disk 2 gb ram <br />\n<br />\n真係好快"},{"pid":"8a1b6d5532582c8c0e8a396e3f7b0eaf0c16667b","tid":1814960,"uid":26436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"水冷先壓得住"},{"pid":"e811dd4b5ea5584ddfc7a1460ea6aabb07c6c7de","tid":1814960,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9635d970e73642146c62cd787025184bcff4e723","tid":1814960,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:26:35.000Z","msg":"250w...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"64C 2.9/4.3GHz 250w咪算係咁"},{"pid":"82873d0a04b7a69ef5d16c328f1480c178aab68c","tid":1814960,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"【蘇媽真狠!!】即場示範 64 核 KO 兩粒 56 核 Xeon<br />\nAMD Threadripper 3990X 2 月 7 日賣街、定價 3990 美元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/18890/%E8%98%87%E5%AA%BD%E7%9C%9F%E7%8B%A0%E5%8D%B3%E5%A0%B4%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84_64_%E6%A0%B8_KO_%E5%85%A9%E7%B2%92_56_%E6%A0%B8_Xeon__AMD_TR_3990X_2_%E6%9C%88_7_%E6%97%A5%E8%B3%A3%E8%A1%97%E5%AE%9A%E5%83%B9_3990_%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F18890%2F%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%258B%25A0%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%25AF%2584_64_%25E6%25A0%25B8_KO_%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25B2%2592_56_%25E6%25A0%25B8_Xeon__AMD_TR_3990X_2_%25E6%259C%2588_7_%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%2583%25B9_3990_%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=feea4877\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/18890/%E8%98%87%E5%AA%BD%E7%9C%9F%E7%8B%A0%E5%8D%B3%E5%A0%B4%E7%A4%BA%E7%AF%84_64_%E6%A0%B8_KO_%E5%85%A9%E7%B2%92_56_%E6%A0%B8_Xeon__AMD_TR_3990X_2_%E6%9C%88_7_%E6%97%A5%E8%B3%A3%E8%A1%97%E5%AE%9A%E5%83%B9_3990_%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83</a><br />\n<br />\n「最強桌面處理器」AMD Threadripper 3990X 正式在 CES 2020 發佈，Ryzen Threadripper 3990X 是全球首款採用 64 核心、128 線程設計的桌面級處理器，「蘇媽」更在現場展示了 3990X 處理器的強大性能對比圖，表示需要三個屏幕才能完整顯示，所以 AMD 以「One CPU to Rule Them All in 2020」的口號去形容 Threadripper 3990X 是完全無錯，它正正就是一款&ldquo;統治眾生&rdquo;的處理器。<br />\n <br />\nAMD Threadripper 3990X 與之前已推出的 Threadripper 3000 系列處理器同樣採用 7nm、Zen 2 架構，擁有高達 64 核心、128線程的恐怖規格，基礎時脈為 2.9GHz，BOOST 加速時脈最高可達 4.3GHz，總緩存達到 288MB，L3 Cache 緩架為 256MB，TDP為 280W，一共有 88 條 PCIe 4 總線，其中 72 條可用。<br />\n<br />\n「蘇媽」在現場展示了 Threadripper 3990X 的 CineBench R20 跑分，並分別與 Threadripper 3950X、3960X、3970X 及 Intel Core i9-9900KS 處理器進行對比，Threadripper 3990X 獲得的 25000+ 分數約等於 24 核心、48 線程 Threadripper 3960X 的兩倍，約等於 8 核心、16 線程的 Intel Core i9-9900KS 的五倍，由於 AMD 用上了棒形圖去進行對比，Threadripper 3990X 竟然是需要三個屏幕才能完整顯示，真猛!!<br />\n <br />\nThreadripper 3990X 的實際效能又有幾強?!「蘇媽」在台上展示 1 顆 US$3,990 的 Threadripper 3990X 對打 2 顆共價值約 US$20,000 的 Xeon Platinum 8280 處理器，在 V-Ray Render 測試結果顯示，2 顆 Xeon Platinum 8280 處理器需要 1 小時 30 分鐘才能完成，而 Threadripper 3990X 只需要 1 小時 3 分鐘就能完成，結果得出 Threadripper 3990X 快上 30% 。<br />\n<br />\n至於售價方面，「最強桌面處理器」AMD Threadripper 3990X 的官方定價為 3990 美元，在 2 月 7 日正式公開發售。"},{"pid":"78335a71bf286efc1d94e31ddade9b05faeb237f","tid":1814960,"uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"Intel垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d0cbc193020228212c0e7d40bbed3ffcfb3699","tid":1814960,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:51:45.000Z","msg":"風扇係咪要長期100%先壓得住?"},{"pid":"1713e6369ade1f2402d89a81431457c544af5635","tid":1814960,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:52:02.000Z","msg":"擁有高達 64 核心、128線程的恐怖規格<br />\n<br />\n約等於 8 核心、16 線程的 Intel Core i9-9900KS 的五倍<br />\n<br />\n即係都係追唔到Intel 14nm?"},{"pid":"0cfe39aa87575d29a59b0fa572fe33976dbe1d86","tid":1814960,"uid":112581,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1713e6369ade1f2402d89a81431457c544af5635","tid":1814960,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:52:02.000Z","msg":"擁有高達 64 核心、128線程的恐怖規格<br />\n<br />\n約等於 8 核心、16 線程的 Intel Core i9-9900KS 的五倍<br />\n<br />\n即係都係追唔到Intel 14nm?"},"citedBy":1,"repl